<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="譯經" xml:id="gsz0712a23shiBuKong"><lb
ed="T" n="0712a23"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0712a23"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042218"><placeName>京兆</placeName><placeName>大興善寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A000095">不空</persName>傳（<persName key="A008843">慧朗</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0712a24"/><persName key="A000095">釋不空</persName>，<name>梵</name>名<persName key="A000095">阿目佉跋折羅</persName>，<name>華</name>言<persName key="A000095">不空金剛</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0712a25"/>止行二字，略也<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n116"/>。本<placeName key="PL000000055420">北天竺</placeName>婆羅門<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g117"/>族<ptr target="#n292"/>，幼失所<lb
ed="T" n="0712a26"/>天<ptr target="#n118"/>，隨叔父觀光<ref type="place" target="#PL000000000083">東國</ref>。<date key="j19836731984037" from-iso="+0719-01-05" to-iso="+0720-01-04">年十五</date><ptr target="#n119"/>，師事<persName key="A000774">金剛智<lb
ed="T" n="0712a27"/>三藏</persName>，初導以<name>梵</name>本悉曇章<ptr type="glossary" target="#g123"/>及聲明論<ptr type="glossary" target="#g124"/>，浹旬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g287"/>已<lb
ed="T" n="0712a28"/>通徹矣。<ref target="#A000774" type="person">師</ref>大異之，與受菩薩戒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g120"/>，引入金剛<lb
ed="T" n="0712a29"/>界大曼荼羅，驗以擲花<ptr target="#n121"/>，知後大興教法。洎<pb ed="T" n="0712b" xml:id="T50.2061.0712b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0712b01"/><ref type="date" target="#j19854951985860">登具戒</ref>，善解一切有部，諳異國書語。<ref type="person" target="#A000774">師</ref>之<lb
ed="T" n="0712b02"/>飜經，常令共譯。凡學聲明論，一紀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g122"/>之功，六月<lb
ed="T" n="0712b03"/>而畢。誦《文殊普賢行願》<ptr target="#n123"/>，一年之限，再夕而終。<lb
ed="T" n="0712b04"/>其敏利皆此類也。欲求學新瑜伽、五部<ptr target="#n124"/>、三密<lb
ed="T" n="0712b05"/>法，<ref type="date" target="#j19854951986590">涉于三載</ref>，<ref target="#A000774" type="person">師</ref>未教詔。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>擬迴<placeName key="PL000000048207">天竺</placeName>，<ref target="#A000774" type="person">師</ref>夢<lb
ed="T" n="0712b06"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京城</ref>諸寺佛菩薩像皆東行，寐寤乃知<persName key="A000095">空</persName>是<lb
ed="T" n="0712b07"/>真法器，遂允所求。<ptr target="#n125"/>授與五部灌頂、護摩<ptr type="glossary" target="#g126"/>、阿<lb
ed="T" n="0712b08"/>闍梨法<ptr type="glossary" target="#g127"/>及《毘盧遮那經》<ptr target="#n128"/>、《蘇悉地軌則》<ptr target="#n129"/>等，盡傳<lb
ed="T" n="0712b09"/>付<ref target="#A000095" type="person">之</ref>。厥後<ref target="#A000774" type="person">師</ref>往<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>，隨侍之際，遇<ref target="#A000774" type="person">其</ref>示滅，<lb
ed="T" n="0712b10"/>即<date key="j19884521988806" from-iso="+0732-02-05" to-iso="+0733-01-24"><name>開元</name>二十年</date>矣<ptr target="#n130"/>。影堂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g131"/>既成，追謚已畢，曾奉<lb
ed="T" n="0712b11"/>遺旨，令往<placeName key="PL000000048207">五天</placeName>并<placeName key="PL000000048734">師子國</placeName>，遂議遐征。</p><p>初至<lb
ed="T" n="0712b12"/><placeName key="PL000000030464">南海郡</placeName>，採訪使<persName key="A008787">劉巨隣</persName>懇請灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>，乃於<placeName key="PL000000030435">法性<lb
ed="T" n="0712b13"/>寺</placeName>相次度人百千萬眾。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>自對<ref target="#A002144" type="person">本尊</ref>祈請<lb
ed="T" n="0712b14"/>旬日，感<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>現身。及將登舟，<ref target="#A008787" type="person">採訪使</ref>召<lb
ed="T" n="0712b15"/>誡<placeName key="PL000000030482">番禺</placeName>界蕃客大首領<persName key="A017844">伊習賓</persName>等曰：「今<persName key="A000095">三藏</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0712b16"/>往<placeName key="PL000000048734"><placeName>南天竺</placeName><placeName>師子國</placeName></placeName>，宜約束船主，好將<persName key="A000095">三藏</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0712b17"/>并弟子<persName key="A000459">含光</persName>、<persName key="A008835"><anchor xml:id="beg0712sgsz1"/>慧𧦬<anchor xml:id="end0712sgsz1"/></persName>等三七人、國信等達彼，無<lb
ed="T" n="0712b18"/>令疎失。」</p><p><date key="j19920851992113" from-iso="+0742-01-16" to-iso="+0742-02-13">二十九年十二月</date>，附<placeName key="PL000000048739">崑崙</placeName><ptr target="#n132"/>舶，離<placeName key="PL000000030464">南<lb
ed="T" n="0712b19"/>海</placeName>至<placeName key="PL000000048202">訶陵國</placeName>界，遇大黑風。眾商惶怖，各作<lb
ed="T" n="0712b20"/>本國法禳之，無驗，皆膜拜求哀，乞加救<lb
ed="T" n="0712b21"/>護，<persName key="A008835">慧𧦪</persName>等亦慟哭。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>曰：「<ref target="#A000095" type="person">吾</ref>今有法，<ref target="#A000459 #A008835" type="person">汝等</ref>勿<lb
ed="T" n="0712b22"/>憂。」遂右手執五股菩提心杵，左手持《般若<lb
ed="T" n="0712b23"/>佛母經》<ptr target="#n133"/>夾，作法誦《大隨求》<ptr target="#n134"/>一遍，即時風偃<lb
ed="T" n="0712b24"/>海澄。又遇大鯨出水，噴浪若山，甚於前<lb
ed="T" n="0712b25"/>患。眾商甘心委命，<persName key="A000095">空</persName>同前作法，令<persName key="A008835">慧𧦪</persName>誦<lb
ed="T" n="0712b26"/>《娑竭龍王經》<ptr target="#n135"/>，逡巡，眾難俱息。</p><p>既達<placeName key="PL000000048734">師子國</placeName><ptr target="#n136"/>，<ref target="#A008837" type="person">王</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0712b27"/>遣使迎<ref target="#A000095" type="person">之</ref>。將入城，步騎羽衛，駢羅衢路。<ref target="#A008837" type="person">王</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0712b28"/>見<persName key="A000095">空</persName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0712sgsz2"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0712sgsz2"/>足請住宮中，七日供養。日以黃金<lb
ed="T" n="0712b29"/>斛滿盛香水，<ref target="#A008837" type="person">王</ref>為<persName key="A000095">空</persName>躬自洗浴，次太子、后<pb ed="T" n="0712c" xml:id="T50.2061.0712c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0712c01"/>妃、輔佐，如<ref target="#A008837" type="person">王</ref>之禮焉。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>始見<persName key="A008836">普賢阿闍梨</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0712c02"/>遂奉獻金寶錦繡之屬，請開十八會<ptr target="#n295"/>《金剛頂》<ptr target="#n137"/><lb
ed="T" n="0712c03"/>瑜伽法門，毘盧遮那大悲胎藏<ptr target="#n138"/>、建立壇法，并<lb
ed="T" n="0712c04"/>許<persName key="A000459">含光</persName>、<persName key="A008835">慧𧦪</persName>等同受五部灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>自爾學<lb
ed="T" n="0712c05"/>無常師，廣求密藏及諸經論五百餘部，本<lb
ed="T" n="0712c06"/>三昧耶<ptr target="#n139"/>、諸尊密印、儀形色像、壇法<anchor xml:id="beg0712002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>幖</sic><corr>標</corr></choice>幟<anchor xml:id="end0712002"/>，文義<lb
ed="T" n="0712c07"/>性相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g583"/>，無不盡源。一日，<ref target="#A008837" type="person">王</ref>作調象戲，人皆登<lb
ed="T" n="0712c08"/>高望之，無敢近者。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>口誦、手印<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n141"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0712sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>作</sic><corr>住</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0712sgsz3"/>於慈定<ptr target="#n142"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0712c09"/>當衢而立，狂象數頭頓皆<anchor xml:id="beg0712sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>踢跌</sic><corr>踼跌</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0712sgsz4"/>，舉國奇之。<lb
ed="T" n="0712c10"/>次遊<placeName key="PL000000048207">五印度</placeName>境，屢彰瑞應。</p><p>至<date key="j19935601993943" from-iso="+0746-01-30" to-iso="+0747-02-17"><name>天寶</name>五載</date>還<lb
ed="T" n="0712c11"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>，進<placeName key="PL000000048734">師子國</placeName>王<persName key="A008837">尸羅迷伽</persName>表及金寶瓔珞，《般<lb
ed="T" n="0712c12"/>若》<name>梵</name>夾、雜珠、白㲲等，奉勅權止<placeName key="PL000000042686">鴻臚</placeName>。續詔入<lb
ed="T" n="0712c13"/>內立壇，為<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>。後移居<placeName key="PL000000042419">淨影寺</placeName>。是歲終<lb
ed="T" n="0712c14"/>夏愆陽<ptr target="#n143"/>，詔令祈雨。制曰：「時不得賒，雨不得<lb
ed="T" n="0712c15"/>暴。」<persName key="A000095">空</persName>奏立孔雀王壇，未盡三日，雨已浹洽。<lb
ed="T" n="0712c16"/><ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>大悅，自持寶箱賜紫袈裟一副，親為披<lb
ed="T" n="0712c17"/>擐，仍賜絹二百匹。後因一日大風卒起，詔<lb
ed="T" n="0712c18"/><persName key="A000095">空</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0712003"/>禳<anchor xml:id="end0712003"/>止，請銀缾一枚作法加持，須臾戢<lb
ed="T" n="0712c19"/>靜<ptr type="glossary" target="#g48"/>。忽因池鵝誤觸缾傾，其風又作，急暴過<lb
ed="T" n="0712c20"/>前，勅令再止，隨止隨効。<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>乃賜號曰<persName key="A000095">智藏</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0712c21"/>焉。</p><p><date key="j19946531995036" from-iso="+0749-01-27" to-iso="+0750-02-14"><name>天寶</name>八載</date>，許迴本國，乘驛騎五匹，至<placeName key="PL000000030464">南<lb
ed="T" n="0712c22"/>海郡</placeName>，有勅再留<ptr target="#n145"/>。<date key="j19961301996483" from-iso="+0753-02-12" to-iso="+0754-01-31">十二載</date>，勅令赴<placeName key="PL000000045074">河</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000046823">隴</placeName>節度<lb
ed="T" n="0712c23"/>使<persName key="A008838">哥舒翰</persName>所請。<date key="j19964841996867" from-iso="+0754-02-01" to-iso="+0755-02-19">十三載</date>，至<placeName key="PL000000045067">武威</placeName>，住<placeName key="PL000000045042">開元寺</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0712c24"/><ref target="#A008838" type="person">節度使</ref>洎賓從皆願受灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>，士庶數千人咸<lb
ed="T" n="0712c25"/>登道場，弟子<persName key="A000459">含光</persName>等亦受五部法。別為功<lb
ed="T" n="0712c26"/>德使開府<persName key="A008839">李元琮</persName>受法，并授金剛界大曼荼<lb
ed="T" n="0712c27"/>羅。是日道場地震，<persName key="A000095">空</persName>曰：「群心之至也。」</p><p><date key="j19972221997399" from-iso="+0756-02-09" to-iso="+0756-08-04">十五載</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0712c28"/>詔還<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>，住<placeName key="PL000000042218">大興善寺</placeName>。<date key="j19974111997576" notBefore-iso="+0756-08-16" notAfter-iso="+0757-01-28"><name>至德</name>初</date>，<ref target="#A004378" type="person">鑾駕</ref>在<placeName key="PL000000047120">靈武</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042848">鳳<lb
ed="T" n="0712c29"/>翔</placeName>，<persName key="A000095">空</persName>常密奉表起居，<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>亦密遣使者求<pb ed="T" n="0713a" xml:id="T50.2061.0713a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0713a01"/>祕密法。<anchor xml:id="beg0713sgsz1"/>洎<anchor xml:id="end0713sgsz1"/>收<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>反正之日，事如所料。<date from-iso="+0758-03-22" key="j19979941998806" to-iso="+0760-06-11"><name>乾元</name></date><lb
ed="T" n="0713a02"/>中，<ref target="#A004378" type="person">帝</ref>請入內，建道場護摩法，為<ref target="#A004378" type="person">帝</ref>受轉輪<lb
ed="T" n="0713a03"/>王<ptr target="#n146"/>位七寶灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>。<date key="j19991631999288" notBefore-iso="+0761-06-03" notAfter-iso="+0761-10-06"><name>上元</name>末</date>，<ref target="#A004378" type="person">帝</ref>不豫，<persName key="A000095">空</persName>以大隨求<lb
ed="T" n="0713a04"/>真言祓除，至七過，翼日乃瘳，<ref target="#A004378" type="person">帝</ref>愈加殊禮<lb
ed="T" n="0713a05"/>焉。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>表請入山，<persName key="A008840">李輔國</persName>宣勅令於<placeName key="PL000000042653">終南山<lb
ed="T" n="0713a06"/>智炬寺</placeName>修功德<ptr target="#n147"/>。念誦之夕，感<persName key="A019615">大樂薩埵</persName>舒<lb
ed="T" n="0713a07"/>毫發光，以相證驗，位隣悉地<ptr target="#n148"/>，<persName key="A000095">空</persName>曰：「眾生未<lb
ed="T" n="0713a08"/>度，<ref target="#A000095" type="person">吾</ref>安自度耶？」</p><p><persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>厭代，<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>即位，恩渥<lb
    ed="T" n="0713a09"/>彌厚。譯《密嚴》<ptr target="#n149"/>、《仁王》<ptr target="#n150"/>二經畢，<ref target="#A004379" type="person">帝</ref>為序焉<ptr target="#n144"/>。頒行<lb
ed="T" n="0713a10"/>之日，慶雲俄現，舉朝表賀。<date key="j20008252000825" when-iso="+0765-12-21"><name>永泰</name>元年十一月<lb
ed="T" n="0713a11"/>一日</date>，制授特進試鴻臚卿，加號<persName key="A000095">大廣智三<lb
ed="T" n="0713a12"/>藏</persName><ptr target="#n151"/>。<date key="j20015932001976" from-iso="+0768-01-28" to-iso="+0769-02-14"><name>大曆</name>三年</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000042218">興善寺</placeName>立道場，勅賜錦繡<lb
ed="T" n="0713a13"/>褥十二領、繡羅<anchor xml:id="beg0713sgsz2"/>幡<anchor xml:id="end0713sgsz2"/>三十二首，又賜道場僧二<lb
ed="T" n="0713a14"/>七日齋糧。勅近侍大臣諸禁軍使並入灌<lb
ed="T" n="0713a15"/>頂。<date from-iso="+0769-11-07" key="j20022422002331" to-iso="+0770-02-04">四年冬</date>，<persName key="A000095">空</persName>奏天下食堂中置<persName key="A002144">文殊菩薩</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0713a16"/>為上座，制許之<ptr target="#n152"/>，此蓋慊<persName key="A009541">憍陳如</persName>是小乘教<lb
ed="T" n="0713a17"/>中始度故也。<date from-iso="+0770-05-04" key="j20024202002507" to-iso="+0770-07-30">五年夏</date>，有詔請<persName key="A000095">空</persName>往<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0713a18"/>修功德，于時彗星出焉。法事告終，星亦隨<lb
ed="T" n="0713a19"/>沒。<date from-iso="+0770-07-31" key="j20025082002595" to-iso="+0770-10-26">秋</date>，<persName key="A000095">空</persName>至自<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>，<ref target="#A004379" type="person">帝</ref>以師子驄并御鞍轡<lb
ed="T" n="0713a20"/>遣中使出城迎入，賜沿道供帳。</p><p><date key="j20029812002981" when-iso="+0771-11-16">六年十月<lb
ed="T" n="0713a21"/>二日</date>，<ref target="#A004379" type="person">帝</ref>誕節，進所譯之經表云：「爰自幼年<lb
ed="T" n="0713a22"/>承事<ref target="#A000774" type="person">先師三藏</ref>十有四載<ptr target="#n153"/>，稟受瑜伽法門。<lb
ed="T" n="0713a23"/>復遊<placeName key="PL000000048207">五印度</placeName>求所未授者，并諸經論，計五<lb
ed="T" n="0713a24"/>百餘部，<date key="j19935601993943" from-iso="+0746-01-30" to-iso="+0747-02-17"><name>天寶</name>五載</date>却至<ref target="#PL000000042189" type="place">上都</ref>。<ref target="#A000291" type="person">上皇</ref>詔入內立<lb
ed="T" n="0713a25"/>灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>道場，所齎<name>梵</name>經盡許飜度。<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>於內<lb
ed="T" n="0713a26"/>立護摩及灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>法。累奉<ref target="#A000291 #A004378" type="person">二聖</ref><ptr target="#n164"/>令鳩聚先代<lb
ed="T" n="0713a27"/>外國<name>梵</name>文，或絛索脫落者修，未譯者譯。<ref target="#A004379" type="person">陛下</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0713a28"/>恭遵遺旨，再使飜傳，利濟群品。起于<date from-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141997399" to-iso="+0756-08-04"><name>天寶</name></date><lb
ed="T" n="0713a29"/>迄今<date key="j20026862003069" from-iso="+0771-01-25" to-iso="+0772-02-12"><name>大曆</name>六年</date>，凡一百二十餘卷，七十七部，<pb ed="T" n="0713b" xml:id="T50.2061.0713b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0713b01"/>并目錄及筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>等僧俗名字，兼略出念誦儀<lb
ed="T" n="0713b02"/>軌，寫畢，遇誕節，謹具進上。」勅付中外，並編<lb
ed="T" n="0713b03"/>入《一切經目錄》中。<persName key="A008841">李憲誠</persName>宣勅賜<persName key="A000095">空</persName>錦綵絹<lb
ed="T" n="0713b04"/>八百匹，同翻經十大德各賜三十匹。沙門<persName key="A001756">潛<lb
ed="T" n="0713b05"/>真</persName>表謝<ptr target="#n154"/>。僧俗弟子賜物有差。</p><p>又以<ref target="#PL000000042189" type="place">京師</ref>春<lb
ed="T" n="0713b06"/>夏不雨<ptr target="#n155"/>，詔<persName key="A000095">空</persName>祈請，如三日內雨，是<ref target="#A000095" type="person">和尚</ref>法<lb
ed="T" n="0713b07"/>力；三日已往而霈然者，非法力也。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>受勅<lb
ed="T" n="0713b08"/>立壇，至第二日大雨云足<ptr target="#n156"/>。<ref target="#A004379" type="person">帝</ref>賜紫羅衣并<lb
ed="T" n="0713b09"/>雜綵百匹，弟子衣七副，設千僧齋，以報功<lb
ed="T" n="0713b10"/>也。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>進表請造<placeName key="PL000000042219">文殊閣</placeName>，勅允奏。<persName key="A017854">貴妃</persName>、<persName key="A017855">韓王</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0713b11"/><persName key="A008842">華陽公主</persName>同成之，捨內庫錢約三千萬計。<lb
ed="T" n="0713b12"/>復翻《孽路荼王經》<ptr target="#n157"/>，宣賜相繼，旁午<ptr type="glossary" target="#g89"/>道路。</p><p>至<lb
ed="T" n="0713b13"/><date from-iso="+0774-02-19" key="j20038072003984" to-iso="+0774-08-15">九年，自春抵夏</date>，宣揚妙法，誡勗門人。每語<lb
ed="T" n="0713b14"/>及《普賢願行》、《出生無邊法門經》<ptr target="#n159"/>，勸令誦持，再<lb
ed="T" n="0713b15"/>三歎息。其先受法者，偏令屬意觀菩提心本<lb
ed="T" n="0713b16"/>尊大印，直<ptr target="#n160"/>詮阿字了法，不生證大覺身，若<lb
ed="T" n="0713b17"/>指諸掌，重重<anchor xml:id="beg0713001"/>囑<anchor xml:id="end0713001"/>累<ptr target="#n161"/>。一夜，命弟子<persName key="A001641">趙遷</persName>：「持筆<lb
ed="T" n="0713b18"/>硯來，<ref target="#A000095" type="person">吾</ref>略出涅槃<anchor xml:id="beg0713002"/>茶毘<anchor xml:id="end0713002"/><ptr target="#n391"/>儀軌以貽後代，<lb
ed="T" n="0713b19"/>使準此送終。」<persName key="A001641">遷</persName>稽首三請「幸乞慈悲久住。<lb
ed="T" n="0713b20"/>不然，眾生何所依乎？」<persName key="A000095">空</persName>笑而已。俄而示疾，<lb
ed="T" n="0713b21"/>上表告辭。勅使勞問，賜醫藥，加開府儀同三<lb
ed="T" n="0713b22"/>司，封<persName key="A000095">肅國公</persName>，食邑三千戶，固讓不俞。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>甚<lb
ed="T" n="0713b23"/>不悅，且曰：「聖眾儼如舒手相慰，白月圓滿，<lb
ed="T" n="0713b24"/><ref target="#A000095" type="person">吾</ref>當逝矣。奈何臨終更竊名位？」乃以五股<lb
ed="T" n="0713b25"/>金剛鈴杵<ref target="#A000774" type="person">先師</ref>所傳者，并銀盤子、菩提子、水<lb
ed="T" n="0713b26"/>精數珠留別，附中使<persName key="A008841">李憲誠</persName>進。<date key="j20039702003970" when-iso="+0774-08-01">六月十五日</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0713b27"/>香水澡沐，東首倚臥，北面瞻望闕庭，以大印<lb
ed="T" n="0713b28"/>身定中而寂，享年七十，僧臘五十。</p><p>弟子<persName key="A008843">慧朗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0713b29"/>次紹灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>之位。餘知法者數人。<ref target="#A004379" type="person">帝</ref>聞，輟視<pb ed="T" n="0713c" xml:id="T50.2061.0713c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0713c01"/>朝三日，賜絹布雜物，錢四十萬，造塔錢二百<lb
ed="T" n="0713c02"/>餘萬<ptr target="#n162"/>。勅功德使<persName key="A008839">李元琮</persName>知護喪事。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>未終<lb
ed="T" n="0713c03"/>前，諸僧夢千仞寶臺摧，文殊新閣<anchor xml:id="beg0713003"/>頹<anchor xml:id="end0713003"/>，金剛<lb
ed="T" n="0713c04"/>杵飛上天。又<placeName key="PL000000042218">興善寺</placeName>後池無故而涸，林竹生<lb
ed="T" n="0713c05"/>實，庭花變萎。<date key="j20039902003990" when-iso="+0774-08-21">七月六日</date><anchor xml:id="beg0713sgsz3"/>茶毘<anchor xml:id="end0713sgsz3"/>，<ref target="#A004379" type="person">帝</ref>詔高品<persName key="A008844"><anchor xml:id="beg0713sgsz4"/>劉<lb
ed="T" n="0713c06"/>僊鶴<anchor xml:id="end0713sgsz4"/></persName>就<ref target="#PL000000042218" type="place">寺</ref>置祭，贈司空，謚曰<persName key="A000095">大辯<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>廣正</sic><corr>正廣</corr></choice>智<lb
ed="T" n="0713c07"/>三藏</persName><ptr target="#n163"/>。火滅，收舍利數百粒。八十粒進內。其頂<lb
ed="T" n="0713c08"/>骨不然，中有舍利一顆，半隱半現，勅於<ref target="#PL000000042218" type="place">本<lb
ed="T" n="0713c09"/>院</ref>別起塔焉。</p><p><persName key="A000095">空</persName>之行化利物居多，於總持<lb
ed="T" n="0713c10"/>門最彰殊勝，測其忍位<ptr type="glossary" target="#g164"/>莫定高卑。始者<persName key="A000291">玄<lb
ed="T" n="0713c11"/>宗</persName>尤推重焉，嘗因歲旱，勅<persName key="A000095">空</persName>祈雨。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>曰：「過<lb
ed="T" n="0713c12"/>某日可禱之，或強得之，其暴可怪。」勅請本<lb
ed="T" n="0713c13"/>師<persName key="A000774">金剛智</persName>設壇，果風雨不止，坊市有漂溺<lb
ed="T" n="0713c14"/>者，樹木有拔仆者。遽詔<persName key="A000095">空</persName>止之。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>於寺庭<lb
ed="T" n="0713c15"/>中揑泥媼<ptr target="#n165"/>五六，溜水作<name>梵</name>言罵之，有頃<lb
ed="T" n="0713c16"/>開霽矣。</p><p><persName key="A000291">玄宗</persName>召術士<persName key="A008845">羅公遠</persName>與<persName key="A000095">空</persName>捔法，同<lb
ed="T" n="0713c17"/>在便殿。<persName key="A000095"><anchor xml:id="beg0713004"/>空<anchor xml:id="end0713004"/></persName>時時反手搔背。<persName key="A008845"><anchor xml:id="beg0713005"/>羅<anchor xml:id="end0713005"/></persName>曰：「借<ref target="#A000095" type="person">尊師</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0713c18"/>如意。」時殿上有<anchor xml:id="beg0713sgsz5"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0713sgsz5"/>石，<persName key="A000095">空</persName>揮如意擊碎於其<lb
ed="T" n="0713c19"/>前，<persName key="A008845">羅</persName>再三取如意不得，<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>欲起取。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>曰：「<persName key="A000291">三<lb
ed="T" n="0713c20"/>郎</persName>勿起，此影耳。」乃舉手示<persName key="A008845">羅</persName>，如意復完然<lb
ed="T" n="0713c21"/>在手<ptr target="#n166"/>。</p><p>又<placeName key="PL000000023510">北邙山</placeName>有巨蛇，樵采者往往見之，<lb
ed="T" n="0713c22"/>矯首若丘陵，夜常承吸露氣。見<persName key="A000095">空</persName>，人語曰：「<lb
ed="T" n="0713c23"/>弟子惡報，<ref target="#A000095" type="person">和尚</ref>如何見度？每欲飜河水陷<lb
ed="T" n="0713c24"/><placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>城以快所懷也。」<persName key="A000095">空</persName>為其受歸戒，說因<lb
ed="T" n="0713c25"/>果，且曰：「汝以瞋心故受，今那復恚恨乎？<ref target="#A000095" type="person">吾</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0713c26"/>力何及？當思<ref target="#A000095" type="person">吾</ref>言，此身必捨矣。」後樵子見<lb
ed="T" n="0713c27"/>蛇死㵎下，臭聞數里。</p><p><persName key="A000095">空</persName>凡應詔祈雨，無他<lb
ed="T" n="0713c28"/>軌則，但設一繡座，手簸旋數寸木神子，念<lb
ed="T" n="0713c29"/>呪擲之。當其自立於座上已，伺其吻角牙<pb ed="T" n="0714a" xml:id="T50.2061.0714a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0714a01"/>出目瞬，則雨至矣。</p><p>又<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141997399" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-04"><name>天寶</name>中</date><ptr target="#n167"/>，<placeName key="PL000000041553">西蕃</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000055088">大石</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000055079">康</placeName>三<lb
ed="T" n="0714a02"/>國帥兵圍<placeName key="PL000000047826">西涼府</placeName>，詔<persName key="A000095">空</persName>入，<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>御于道場。<persName key="A000095">空</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0714a03"/>秉香<anchor xml:id="beg0714sgsz1"/>罏<anchor xml:id="end0714sgsz1"/>，誦《仁王》密語二七遍，<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>見神兵可<lb
ed="T" n="0714a04"/>五百員在于殿庭，驚問<persName key="A000095">空</persName>。<persName key="A000095">空</persName>曰：「<persName key="A004261">毘沙門天<lb
ed="T" n="0714a05"/>王</persName>子領兵救<placeName key="PL000000047826">安西</placeName>，請急設食發遣。」<date key="j19922211992221" when-iso="+0742-06-01">四月二<lb
ed="T" n="0714a06"/>十日</date><ptr target="#n168"/>果奏云：「<date key="j19921541992154" when-iso="+0742-03-26">二月十一日</date>。<placeName key="PL000000047826">城</placeName>東北三十許里，<lb
ed="T" n="0714a07"/>雲霧間見神兵長偉，鼓角諠鳴，山地崩震，蕃<lb
ed="T" n="0714a08"/>部驚潰。彼營壘中有鼠金色，咋弓弩弦皆<lb
ed="T" n="0714a09"/>絕。城北門樓有<persName key="A004261">光明天王</persName>怒視，蕃帥大奔。」<ptr target="#n169"/><lb
ed="T" n="0714a10"/><ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>覽奏謝<persName key="A000095">空</persName>，因勅諸道城樓置<persName key="A004261">天王</persName>像，此<lb
ed="T" n="0714a11"/>其始也。</p><p><persName key="A000095">空</persName>既終，三朝所賜墨制一皆進納<ptr target="#n170"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0714a12"/>生榮死哀，<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>傳法僧至此，今古少類矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0714a13"/>嗣其法位，<persName key="A008843">慧朗</persName>師也。御史大夫<persName key="A008846">嚴郢</persName>為碑，<lb
ed="T" n="0714a14"/><persName key="A008847">徐浩</persName>書之，樹於<ref target="#PL000000042218" type="place">本院</ref>焉。</p>
    <p><lb
ed="T" n="0714a15"/>系曰：傳教令輪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g100"/>者，<placeName key="PL000000000083">東夏</placeName>以<persName key="A000774">金剛智</persName>為始祖，<lb
ed="T" n="0714a16"/><persName key="A000095">不空</persName>為二祖，<persName key="A008843">慧朗</persName>為三祖，已下宗承所損<lb
ed="T" n="0714a17"/>益可知也。自後岐分派別。</p><p>咸曰<ptr target="#n762"/>：「傳瑜伽大<lb
ed="T" n="0714a18"/>教，多則多矣，而少驗者何？」亦猶羽嘉生應<lb
ed="T" n="0714a19"/>龍，應龍生鳳皇，凰皇已降，生庶鳥矣<ptr target="#n171"/>。欲無<lb
ed="T" n="0714a20"/>變革，其可得乎！</p>
